An official Artists Across Amia membership card, the sign of membership in this exclusive community of creative entrepreneurs, enthusiasts, patrons, professional performers and art aficianados. The glossy surface is customized with your name stencilled in clear black calligraphy on a decorative white background, just beneath the broad line reading "Artists Across Amia: Exclusive Membership Card". The border is dressed in artfully rendered theater curtains with a rich velvety texture that shift prismatically in rainbow color as the card is tilted in the light. The back of the card is a small reprinting of an immaculate diorama of colors, shapes, and patterns; within the diorama, the skilled artist's eye can pick out a creative combination of the holy symbols belonging to Oghma, Lliira, Milil, and Gond. 

Flash this card at specific events to gain free or discounted admittance, preferential box seating, and other special considerations.
